  "projectType": "api-service",
  "projectName": "Apache Fineract",
  "projectDescription": "Apache Fineract is a multi-tenant, modular Spring Boot core banking platform for microfinance, lending, savings, accounting, and financial inclusion, exposing a large REST API backed by Liquibase-managed MySQL/MariaDB/PostgreSQL schemas, a CQRS-style command framework, a Spring Batch close-of-business engine, and pluggable external event/notification integrations.",
