  "keyFeatures": [
    "fineract-core: shared domain, infrastructure, JPA, serialization, JSON command framework, tenant routing",
    "fineract-security: Basic auth, OAuth2 authorization server, tenant-aware filters, 2FA",
    "fineract-command: CQRS-style command source, idempotency, maker-checker, command handler registry",
    "fineract-validation: data validators and Jakarta constraint validators",
    "fineract-cob: Spring Batch close-of-business engine with pluggable BusinessSteps and account locking",
    "fineract-accounting: GL accounts, journal entries, accrual postings, closure, provisioning entries, accounting rules, trial balance",
    "fineract-loan: loan domain, charges, schedule generation, transaction processors, delinquency, reschedule, interest pauses, guarantors, collateral",
    "fineract-progressive-loan: progressive amortization, recalculation, buy-down fee, capitalized income",
    "fineract-progressive-loan-embeddable-schedule-generator: standalone progressive schedule generator",
    "fineract-loan-origination: loan originator domain and APIs",
    "fineract-working-capital-loan: working capital loan product, calc engine, COB integration",
    "fineract-savings: savings, charges, fixed deposit, recurring deposit, GSIM group savings, interest posting jobs",
    "fineract-investor: external asset owner transfers, loan product attributes, accounting integration, COB step",
    "fineract-branch: teller, cashier, teller journal",
    "fineract-document: document management, images, S3 / filesystem content store, detectors, policies",
    "fineract-charge: portfolio charges domain and APIs",
    "fineract-tax: tax components, tax groups",
    "fineract-rates: floating rates",
    "fineract-report: report providers and report-mailing-job",
    "fineract-mix: MIX Market reporting taxonomy and mapping",
    "fineract-provider: Spring Boot application assembly, Jersey REST APIs, Hikari/JDBC config, security config",
    "fineract-war: WAR packaging of the provider for external servlet containers",
    "fineract-client / fineract-client-feign: generated REST SDKs",
    "fineract-avro-schemas: Avro definitions for external events",
    "fineract-db: legacy SQL bootstrap and demo tenant backups",
    "fineract-doc: Asciidoc/Antora documentation source",
    "Portfolio: clients, groups, centers, calendars, meetings, notes, funds, transfers, collateral, account transfers, standing instructions",
    "Organisation: offices, staff, holidays, working days, currencies, provisioning categories and criteria",
    "User administration: users, roles, permissions, password policy, self-service users",
    "Notification: Spring and ActiveMQ event publisher/listener, notification API, cache",
    "Batch API: multi-action HTTP batch endpoint with command strategies and dependency resolution",
    "Scheduling: Quartz scheduler, inline job runner, Spring Batch manager/worker, stuck job recovery",
    "External events: business events, external event domain, JMS and Kafka producers, idempotent dispatch, Avro serializers",
    "Hooks: web hooks, Twilio, Elasticsearch, message gateway, hook processors",
    "Campaigns: email and SMS campaigns, SMS gateway scheduler, configuration",
    "Data queries: datatables, entity datatable checks, reports, run-reports, exports",
    "Surveys / SPM: surveys, likelihood, poverty line, SPM scorecards",
    "Credit bureau and adhoc query",
    "Interoperation: PISP-style interop API and domain",
    "Multi-tenancy: tenant master DB + per-tenant routing, Hikari per tenant, business-date and COB-date context",
    "Liquibase changelogs split across modules and tenant vs tenant-store databases",
    "Configuration: application.properties, global configuration API, external services config, feature flags, instance mode",
    "Docker compose profiles (MariaDB, MySQL, PostgreSQL, ActiveMQ, Kafka, web app) and Jib container build",
    "Kubernetes deployment manifests",
    "Integration tests, OAuth2 tests, 2FA tests, Cucumber E2E suite with 80+ feature files",
    "Custom modules ('custom/<company>/<category>/<module>' dynamic Gradle inclusion) with acme example",
    "Static EclipseLink JPA weaving via static-weaving.gradle"
  ],
